Stacktrace
sbt.ForkMain$ForkError: org.scalatest.exceptions.TestFailedDueToTimeoutException: The code passed to failAfter did not complete within 60 seconds.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
